A palindrome is a word, phrase, or sequence that reads
the same backwards as forwards, e.g. madam or nurses run.
Develop the following code:
Define the isPalindrome action that receives a word and checks
whether it is a palindrome and returns true or false.
Define a collection of words.
Write a code that checks a collection of words and says the ones
that are palindromes.
Available actions: getWordsMixedWithPalindromes()